2 TITL map Norge-Värmland-Västra Götaland border
1 _OID 8b2a6042-2594-4d60-b5bb-db34e438a8a0
1 _DSCR Map view of the borderland: [on. L] Norway, with Värmland to the North & Västra Götaland (Älvsborgs län bef 1998) to the South. Very complex border! Parishes underlined red, & important early farmsteads underlined blue: Viker (Trankil), Öbyn (Bloms
2 CONC kog) & Svensbyn (Sillerud) in Värmland; Alsbyn & Södra Kölviken (Torrskog), & Valsebo (Nössemark) in Västra Götaland ["Western Gothland" included Värmland & was ethnically distinct from Svealand to the North]
1 _META <metadataxml><transcription>Yej!!! Goths rule!!!
2 CONT 
2 CONT Fun fact - Actress Julia Roberts&apos; mother&apos;s family came from Eganäs, Sillerud, Värmland</transcription></metadataxml>
